<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>One-Time Password Verification</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', 'Fira Sans', 'Droid Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fafafa 0%, #ffffff 100%);
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
        }
        .header {
            padding: 40px 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: #000000;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 40px 40px;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #444444;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .otp-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #999999;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .otp-code {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #333333 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            padding: 24px 48px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;
            user-select: all;
        }
        .otp-hint {
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #fff9e6;
            border: 1px solid #ffe58f;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #664d03;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .info-box strong {
            color: #332701;
        }
        .security-tips {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        .security-tips h3 {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .security-tips ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .security-tips li {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #555555;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .security-tips li::before {
            content: '‚úì';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #00aa00;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 32px 40px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px auto;
                border-radius: 0;
                border-left: none;
                border-right: none;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding-left: 24px;
                padding-right: 24px;
            }
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 36px;
                letter-spacing: 8px;
                padding: 20px 32px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">üîë</div>
            <h1>Verify Your Identity</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Enter the code below to continue</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="message">
                To ensure the security of your account, please use the verification code below. This code is unique to your request and will expire soon.
            </p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <div class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</div>
                <div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>
                <div class="otp-hint">Click to select and copy</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>‚è± Important:</strong> This code will expire in <strong>{{expiry}}</strong>. Do not share this code with anyone.
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h3>Security Tips</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Never share your verification code with anyone</li>
                    <li>Our team will never ask for your code</li>
                    <li>If you didn't request this code, ignore this email</li>
                    <li>Use this code only on our official website or app</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>¬© 2025 FD Auth. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
